{"type":"message","id":"706b0323","parentId":"aee35561","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:00:00.200Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:8ecc8a2f-8c0c-47da-b813-78ecc92e2cd5 每日新闻与市场早报] 执行每日新闻与市场早报任务：\n\n0. 查询西安今日天气，生成天气简报，重点给出穿衣建议，提醒是否需要带伞\n\n1. 国际新闻TOP5：使用 web_search 搜索\"国际新闻\"、\"世界新闻\"、\"global news\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n2. 国内新闻TOP5：使用 web_search 搜索\"国内新闻\"、\"中国新闻\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n3. 半导体行业新闻：使用 web_search 搜索\"半导体行业新闻\"、\"WiFi芯片\"、\"芯片验证\"、\"ESP32\"、\"乐鑫\"，输出10条行业新闻摘要\n\n4. 乐鑫科技(688018)股票分析：获取最新股价、涨跌幅、成交量，搜索公司公告、研报、最新消息，给出持有/卖出的建议\n\n5. 股票推荐TOP5：使用 web_search 搜索\"股票推荐\"、\"买入评级\"、\"券商推荐股票\"，推荐10个值得关注的股票及理由\n\n6. 基金推荐TOP5：使用 web_search 搜索\"基金推荐\"、\"优质基金\"、\"基金排行\"，推荐10个值得买入的基金及理由\n\n7. openclaw，claude code及其同类产品的最新进展\n\n**重要步骤**：\n1. 使用 feishu_doc create 创建飞书文档\n2. 使用 feishu_doc write 将完整内容写入文档（这一步必须执行！）\n3. 获取文档链接\n4. 发送飞书卡片消息，附上文档链接\n\n**搜索工具要求**：\n- 必须使用 web_search (Tavily)，返回的链接是真实 URL\n- 不要使用百度搜索（返回的是跳转链接）\n- 确保每条新闻的链接是可直接访问的完整域名\n\n输出要求：\n- 使用飞书卡片格式\n- 同时将所有信息整理成一个飞书文档，将飞书文档链接附在飞书卡片最后\n- 每个部分用清晰标题分隔\n- 重要信息加粗\n- 股票/基金推荐包含代码/名称+推荐理由\n- 每条新闻/信息必须附上来源和链接\n- 格式：📰 [新闻标题] - [一句话摘要]\n        🔗 来源：[网站名称] | [完整URL，必须是可直接访问的链接]\n- 如果某条信息无法找到确切来源，标注\"来源待确认\"\n\n完成后通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 07:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-01 23:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775084400195}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c6cdad5","parentId":"706b0323","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:00:25.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行一个每日新闻与市场早报的定时任务。让我梳理一下需要做的事情：\n\n1. 查询西安天气\n2. 国际新闻TOP5\n3. 国内新闻TOP5\n4. 半导体行业新闻\n5. 乐鑫科技股票分析\n6. 股票推荐TOP5\n7. 基金推荐TOP5\n8. OpenClaw/Claude Code等产品的最新进展\n\n然后：\n- 创建飞书文档\n- 写入内容\n- 获取文档链接\n- 发送飞书卡片消息给用户 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\n\n首先，我需要查看一下天气技能，然后进行所有的搜索工作，最后整合成文档发送。\n\n让我先读取weather技能，然后开始并行执行搜索任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"开始执行每日新闻与市场早报任务。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_de0c5dd0ba6b481290771389","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:/Users/LWS/AppData/Roaming/npm/node_modules/openclaw/skills/weather/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_14327a1b1c724a1db5ca5f1e","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"西安天气预报 今日穿衣指数","count":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a16f5d88213e41ef87ab7084","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"国际新闻 global news today world news","count":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b50915cce04e4cd0beff60ca","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"国内新闻 中国新闻","count":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ac686787cfe54b25afcf39c9","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"半导体行业新闻 WiFi芯片 芯片验证 ESP32 乐鑫","count":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":22230,"output":491,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22721,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775084400200,"responseId":"2a688e912435f05b7d035d90455194c4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc0a2ea2","parentId":"7c6cdad5","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:00:25.896Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_de0c5dd0ba6b481290771389","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: weather\ndescription: \"Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo. Use when: user asks about weather, temperature, or forecasts for any location. NOT for: historical weather data, severe weather alerts, or detailed meteorological analysis. No API key needed.\"\nhomepage: https://wttr.in/:help\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"☔\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"curl\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"curl\",\n              \"bins\": [\"curl\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install curl (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Weather Skill\n\nGet current weather conditions and forecasts.\n\n## When to Use\n\n✅ **USE this skill when:**\n\n- \"What's the weather?\"\n- \"Will it rain today/tomorrow?\"\n- \"Temperature in [city]\"\n- \"Weather forecast for the week\"\n- Travel planning weather checks\n\n## When NOT to Use\n\n❌ **DON'T use this skill when:**\n\n- Historical weather data → use weather archives/APIs\n- Climate analysis or trends → use specialized data sources\n- Hyper-local microclimate data → use local sensors\n- Severe weather alerts → check official NWS sources\n- Aviation/marine weather → use specialized services (METAR, etc.)\n\n## Location\n\nAlways include a city, region, or airport code in weather queries.\n\n## Commands\n\n### Current Weather\n\n```bash\n# One-line summary\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=3\"\n\n# Detailed current conditions\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?0\"\n\n# Specific city\ncurl \"wttr.in/New+York?format=3\"\n```\n\n### Forecasts\n\n```bash\n# 3-day forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London\"\n\n# Week forecast\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n\n# Specific day (0=today, 1=tomorrow, 2=day after)\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?1\"\n```\n\n### Format Options\n\n```bash\n# One-liner\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+%w\"\n\n# JSON output\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=j1\"\n\n# PNG image\ncurl \"wttr.in/London.png\"\n```\n\n### Format Codes\n\n- `%c` — Weather condition emoji\n- `%t` — Temperature\n- `%f` — \"Feels like\"\n- `%w` — Wind\n- `%h` — Humidity\n- `%p` — Precipitation\n- `%l` — Location\n\n## Quick Responses\n\n**\"What's the weather?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%t+(feels+like+%f),+%w+wind,+%h+humidity\"\n```\n\n**\"Will it rain?\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl -s \"wttr.in/London?format=%l:+%c+%p\"\n```\n\n**\"Weekend forecast\"**\n\n```bash\ncurl \"wttr.in/London?format=v2\"\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- No API key needed (uses wttr.in)\n- Rate limited; don't spam requests\n- Works for most global cities\n- Supports airport codes: `curl wttr.in/ORD`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775084425894}}
{"type":"message","id":"b076d51d","parentId":"fc0a2ea2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:00:27.685Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_14327a1b1c724a1db5ca5f1e","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"西安天气预报 今日穿衣指数\",\n  \"provider\": \"firecrawl\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1794,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"firecrawl\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b374afbcf7c458de\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n穿衣指数-西安-中国天气网-专业天气预报、气象服务门户\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b374afbcf7c458de\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.weather.com.cn/indexfc/ct/101110101.shtml\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d1c7519bb8a33435\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n天气网建议: 天气炎热，建议着短衫、短裙、短裤、薄型T恤衫、敞领短袖棉衫等清凉夏季服装。 炎热 温度：25摄氏度风向： 东北风 风速：2级相对湿度：57% 发布时间： 2014年07 ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d1c7519bb8a33435\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"weather.com.cn\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"53edbeea92bfc1ad\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n西安天气预报15天天气穿衣指数\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"53edbeea92bfc1ad\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.tianqi.com/xian/chuanyi.html\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d846bd1ca34fdf78\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n西安. [切换城市] · 今天. 多云. 10℃~25℃. 东北风2级. 穿衣指数：白天天气良好，建议穿薄型套装等服装。 明天. 阴转多云. 13℃~17℃. 西南风2级. 穿衣指数：白天天气良好，建议穿 ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d846bd1ca34fdf78\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"tianqi.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"05afeab858f0b9c4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n陕西省, 西安天气预报 - MSN\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"05afeab858f0b9c4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.msn.com/zh-cn/weather/foreca